snippet.title: Mortal Kombat 1 – Official Homelander Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Let's light this candle. Homelander lands in Mortal Kombat 1 on June 4 for early access players. Ferra joins the Kameo roster later in June.

Play as Homelander on June 4 and jump into Mortal Kombat 1 now:
https://www.mortalkombat.com/purchase 

It's In Our Blood. Discover a reborn Mortal Kombat Universe created by Fire God Liu Kang. Mortal Kombat 1 ushers in a new era of the iconic franchise with a new fighting system, game modes, and Fatalities!
